### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### Get all products filtered by name
GET http://localhost:3000/products?name=key

### Get all products sorted by price
GET http://localhost:3000/products?sort=price

### Get single product
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1

### Get product that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/999

### Add a new product
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monitor",
  "price": 199.99,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Add product missing required field (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Broken Item"
}

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 59.99
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/2
